| State | Steps                                          | Action                                                                  | info                                                    |
|-------+------------------------------------------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------+---------------------------------------------------------|
| DONE  | Create app                                     | npx create-react-project proj-name                                      | If npx with node, npx autoInstall create-react-project  |
|       |                                                |                                                                         | commande in first launch                                |
|-------+------------------------------------------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------+---------------------------------------------------------|
| DONE  | Create folders                                 | src/(components, redux(...), screens, utils)                            |                                                         |
|       |                                                | Move app to src, update index.js                                        |                                                         |
|-------+------------------------------------------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------+---------------------------------------------------------|
| DONE  | Launch app with emulator                       |                                                                         |                                                         |
|-------+------------------------------------------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------+---------------------------------------------------------|
| DONE  | Enable .jsx extensions,                        | resolver: { sourceExts: ['jsx', 'js', 'json', 'ts', 'tsx'], }, };       | ← add code to metro.config.js                           |
|       | and babel linter                               | add: "parser": "@babel/eslint-parser" to .eslintrc and install          | watchman watch-del-all                                  |
|       |                                                | $ npm install @babel/eslint-parser                                      | watchman shutdown-server                                |
|-------+------------------------------------------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------+---------------------------------------------------------|
| DONE  | Install redux, config it                       | $ npm install redux                                                     |                                                         |
|       |                                                | $ npm install react-redux                                               |                                                         |
|       |                                                | $ npm install redux-thunk                                               |                                                         |
|       |                                                | Create redux/ dirs and create (actions, reducer and store)              |                                                         |
|-------+------------------------------------------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------+---------------------------------------------------------|
| DONE  | Install react-native vector fonts              | $ npm install --save react-native-vector-icons                          |                                                         |
|       | Add following line lo android/app/build.gradle | apply from: "../../node_modules/react-native-vector-icons/fonts.gradle" |                                                         |
|       | Go to android to sync gradle with follow cmd → | $ ./gradlew clean                                                       |                                                         |
|-------+------------------------------------------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------+---------------------------------------------------------|
| DONE  | Install Navigation and config                  | npm install @react-navigation/native                                    | I tend to use tab navigation                            |
|       | Work with React-Native CLI →                   | npm install react-native-screens react-native-safe-area-context         | https://reactnavigation.org/docs/getting-started/       |
|       | I plan to use tab navigation →                 | npm install @react-navigation/bottom-tabs                               |                                                         |
|-------+------------------------------------------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------+---------------------------------------------------------|
| DONE  | Install Notification and config it             | $ npm install --save react-native-push-notification                     |                                                         |
|       |                                                | add some change to android/build.gradle from github                     |                                                         |
|-------+------------------------------------------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------+---------------------------------------------------------|
|       | Install and config Camera.                     | $ npm install react-native-camera --save                                | Add follow code to app/build.gragradle too, to avoid    |
|       |                                                | add some config from github in main/Manifest... and app/build.gradle    | multiDex error when sync gradle: 'multiDexEnabled true' |
|       |                                                | $ npm install --save react-native-camera-hooks                          |                                                         |
|       |                                                | $ npm install react-native-fs --save  // This module allow us to save   | our capture from camera to desire location.             |
|       | Go to android folder to sync gradle with →     | $ ./gradlew clean // goback project folder then reload app and emulator |                                                         |
